show.description: Selena was tricked into having a child with Louis, but her sister Dayana took the baby and lied about its death. Years later, Selena returns and reunites with Yusuf and the child. When Dyana's abuse of the child is uncovered, she causes a car accident in a panic. Louis then learns that Selena is the biological mother of his child, and the family comes together to live happily.
